UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Riverside County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%riverside%' AND name != 'Riverside County EMS Agency');
